******
[3]
Date: 23 Jul 2015
Source: Focus Information Agency [edited]
http://www.focus-fen.net/news/2015/07/23/378617/all-anthrax-prone-retail-stores-are-being-disinfected-varna-district-governor.html


Disinfection of all retail stores in Varna district that are thought to be [contaminated with _Bacillus anthracis_] is completed. That is what Varna district governor Stoyan Pasev said to Radio FOCUS - Varna.The emergency operation for disinfection of retail stores and restaurants against anthrax disease was carried out last night.

After a meeting of the Crisis Staff at the District Administration, the number of the anthrax-suspected retail shops and restaurants was reduced to 23: 2 of the anthrax [contamination]-prone retail stores are in Kranevo village, Dobrich Municipality; 1 is in Byala village; 6 of the anthrax [contamination] -prone restaurants are in Golden Beach resort; and all the remaining 14 are in the territory of the town of Varna. All the 23 shops, fast-food booths, and restaurants have been closed.

